text: Alenka Hubacek (born 24 November 1990) is an Australian female tennis player. Hubacek has a career high WTA singles ranking of 460, achieved on 8 February 2010. She also has a career high WTA doubles ranking of 274 achieved on 27 September 2010. Hubacek has won four ITF doubles titles.
